    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Shinigami Clan, Level 8+<br />Your Zanpakutō can never be sealed once gaining its true form, granting it stunted growth, but more base power. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li>Increase your Intelligence or Dexterity score by +1, to a maximum of 20.</li><li>You gain 5 more Shikai Points to distribute.</li><li>You gain an additional 2 Shikai Points at 11th, and 18th level.</li><li>If you take this feat past 11th or 18th level you instead gain an additional 1 Shikai Point for each level passed.</li><li>You cannot take the Constant Release Shikai feat.</li></ul>",
